title: Pakistani lawmakers elect Shahbaz Sharif as new premier - The Associated Press
content: Pakistani lawmakers elect Shahbaz Sharif as new premier  The Associated PressView Full Coverage on Google News
description: ISLAMABAD (AP) — Pakistan’s parliament elected opposition lawmaker Shahbaz Sharif as the new prime minister Monday, following a week of political turmoil that led to the weekend ouster of Premier Imran Khan.
